column2: SELECT TOP # s.z,s.specObjID, ph.objID, p.absMagU, p.absMagG, p.absMagR, p.absMagI, p.absMagZ, gi.d4#, gs.oii_#_reqw, gs.oii_#_eqw, gs.oii_#_reqw, gs.oii_#_eqw, gs.h_delta_reqw, gs.h_delta_eqw, gs.h_gamma_reqw, gs.h_gamma_eqw, gs.h_beta_reqw, gs.h_beta_eqw, gs.oiii_#_eqw, gs.oiii_#_reqw, gs.oiii_#_eqw, gs.h_alpha_reqw, gs.h_alpha_eqw FROM SpecObj as s  JOIN PhotoObj as ph ON ph.objID =s.bestObjID  JOIN galSpecIndx as gi ON s.specObjID= gi.specObjID  JOIN galSpecLine as gs ON s.specObjID= gs.specObjID  JOIN Photoz as p ON s.bestObjID= p.objid WHERE s.z<# ,galSpecLine.h_gamma_reqw ,galSpecLine.h_gamma_eqw ,galSpecLine.h_beta_reqw ,galSpecLine.h_beta_eqw ,galSpecLine.oiii_#_eqw ,galSpecLine.oiii_#_reqw ,galSpecLine.oiii_#_eqw ,galSpecLine.h_alpha_reqw ,galSpecLine.h_alpha_eqw FROM SpecObjAll JOIN GalaxyTag ON SpecObjAll.bestObjID=GalaxyTag.specObjID JOIN Photoz ON GalaxyTag.objID=Photoz.objID JOIN galSpecIndx ON galSpecIndx.specObjID=SpecObjAll.specObjID JOIN galSpecLine ON galSpecLine.specObjID=SpecObjAll.specObjID WHERE SpecObjAll.z BETWEEN # AND #
